OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy start but
OL,6,Fstaying dry through the day with some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny intervals developing.
OL,8,FFeeling warm, especially in the east.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry evening with bright
OL,11,Fspells. Cloud will thicken overnight
OL,12,Fwith some patchy rain spreading in
OL,13,Ffrom the west by the morning.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSunday:FA rather cloudy start with
OL,16,Fsome patchy light rain. Becoming dry
OL,17,Fwith some long spells of sunshine by
OL,18,Fthe afternoon. Another warm day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
